ResizeHD
============
ResizeHD is app for resize all image @2x and -hd to half. It's very util for resize all images from retina display and images used in cocos2d.

[http://www.bakingcode.com](www.bakingcode.com)

Using ResizeHD
===================================

1. Open ResizeHD.app
2. Drag and drop your images into app
3. And you images save automatically in source folder.
